WEBVTT

00:00:18.419 --> 00:00:19.936
So, here.

00:00:20.736 --> 00:00:22.019
There used to be a tattoo here.

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:23.920
But this person had it removed.

00:00:24.760 --> 00:00:28.260
We reconstructed it based on
the remnants and gaps in the pattern.

00:00:31.359 --> 00:00:32.780
This is the pattern we got.

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:36.600
So, the conclusion is
this person got a tattoo.

00:00:36.600 --> 00:00:37.700
And it wasn't well done.

00:00:38.280 --> 00:00:40.039
Then he had it removed. That's all.

00:00:40.859 --> 00:00:42.560
Captain Li, the picture is printed.

00:00:45.259 --> 00:00:46.899
Captain Li, don't say that.

00:00:48.060 --> 00:00:50.240
(Knife)
It's still a detail, no matter what.

00:00:54.119 --> 00:00:54.759
Knife.

00:00:56.020 --> 00:00:56.619
Knife.

00:00:59.039 --> 00:01:01.240
Captain Li,
want to go for a walk with me?

00:01:03.859 --> 00:01:04.900
I'll show you

00:01:05.719 --> 00:01:07.400
how a dead man can be revived.

00:02:18.848 --> 00:02:21.568
=The Silent Rift=

00:02:21.824 --> 00:02:24.552
=Episode 6=
(Invalid Evidence)

00:02:24.960 --> 00:02:27.680
All kinds of stationery
and toys available.

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:29.379
Hula hoops and pushcarts.

00:02:29.479 --> 00:02:32.400
Also new temporary tattoos.
Buy more, get more free!

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:34.620
Back-to-school sale! Buy more, get more!

00:02:37.979 --> 00:02:38.599
Sir.

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:41.120
Ma'am, do you have
any other temporary tattoos?

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:42.599
Yes, I'll get them for you.

00:02:44.240 --> 00:02:45.319
Please sit. Take your time.

00:02:55.541 --> 00:02:57.792
(Endurance)

00:02:58.759 --> 00:02:59.819
You like this one?

00:02:59.819 --> 00:03:01.824
(Endurance)

00:03:05.039 --> 00:03:05.680
How much?

00:03:15.319 --> 00:03:15.960
Xu Ming.

00:03:17.539 --> 00:03:18.180
Xu Ming.

00:03:19.759 --> 00:03:20.460
It's me, Zhu.

00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:22.039
Don't be afraid.

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:23.900
Xu Ming.

00:03:24.319 --> 00:03:25.180
Knife, knife.

00:03:25.900 --> 00:03:26.620
Take a look.

00:03:26.620 --> 00:03:27.120
Knife.

00:03:27.419 --> 00:03:29.400
Is this the knife you saw
at the scene back then?

00:03:31.319 --> 00:03:32.460
Xu Ming, look.

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:35.259
Xu Ming, take a look.

00:03:35.819 --> 00:03:36.479
Just look.

00:03:37.180 --> 00:03:38.400
Is it this knife?

00:03:40.259 --> 00:03:40.759
Knife.

00:03:41.440 --> 00:03:42.752
(Knife)

00:03:47.599 --> 00:03:48.620
Knife! Knife!

00:03:48.620 --> 00:03:49.599
- Xu Ming.
- It's okay.

00:03:49.599 --> 00:03:51.259
Knife! Knife!

00:03:51.259 --> 00:03:51.759
Xu Ming.

00:03:51.759 --> 00:03:52.340
Knife!

00:03:52.340 --> 00:03:53.180
Xu Ming, let go.

00:03:53.740 --> 00:03:54.340
Let go.

00:03:55.900 --> 00:03:56.960
Let go. Nurse!

00:03:57.539 --> 00:03:58.259
Nurse!

00:03:59.539 --> 00:04:00.259
- Xu Ming.
- Nurse!

00:04:00.259 --> 00:04:00.879
Out first.

00:04:00.879 --> 00:04:01.819
Please step out.

00:04:02.539 --> 00:04:03.319
Don't agitate him.

00:04:03.319 --> 00:04:04.039
Let go, Xu Ming.

00:04:09.599 --> 00:04:11.539
It's okay now. It's okay.

00:04:11.759 --> 00:04:12.479
It's okay.

00:04:20.899 --> 00:04:22.839
Captain Li, are you alright?

00:04:23.519 --> 00:04:24.339
I think...

00:04:25.779 --> 00:04:27.399
I think I might remember something.

00:04:27.620 --> 00:04:28.240
Yes.

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:29.959
I remember now.

00:04:32.704 --> 00:04:35.264
(Crack down on crime.
Protect the people.)

00:04:38.899 --> 00:04:39.680
Wang Dazhu.

00:04:44.079 --> 00:04:45.500
Look, what's this?

00:04:46.019 --> 00:04:48.060
The reconstructed image
of the tattoo on your arm.

00:04:53.984 --> 00:04:55.296
(Knife)

00:04:56.339 --> 00:04:57.339
What? I don't get it.

00:04:59.060 --> 00:04:59.899
You don't get it?

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:03.620
What? Tried to be like Meng Guangcai

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:05.779
and be the big boss, huh?

00:05:05.779 --> 00:05:09.019
You wanted "endurance", but chickened
out, so only "knife" is left.

00:05:10.019 --> 00:05:11.300
Where did you put the "heart"?

00:05:13.180 --> 00:05:14.060
So what?

00:05:15.180 --> 00:05:16.620
What's wrong with no "heart"?

00:05:17.279 --> 00:05:18.839
An eyewitness identified

00:05:20.060 --> 00:05:23.180
that one criminal
had the exact tattoo back then.

00:05:25.560 --> 00:05:27.060
Who?

00:05:29.399 --> 00:05:33.120
I wore long sleeves year-round.
Who could see my tattoo?

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:36.064
The crime happened in summer.
Seeing a tattoo is normal.

00:05:36.064 --> 00:05:37.959
You might've been seen without knowing.

00:05:38.779 --> 00:05:41.639
I didn't know? I didn't know?

00:05:42.500 --> 00:05:45.060
They had their hoods pulled down tight.

00:05:45.060 --> 00:05:47.360
How could he see the tattoo?

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:52.680
Wang Dazhu, the fact that the suspects
wore masks is police confidential.

00:05:52.680 --> 00:05:53.899
How did you know that?

00:05:56.959 --> 00:05:58.496
Unless you were part of the 6.10 case.

00:06:03.139 --> 00:06:04.120
Tricking me?

00:06:05.740 --> 00:06:07.459
Trying to get a confession
out of me, huh?

00:06:08.500 --> 00:06:11.060
If you weren't part of it,
how would you know these details?

00:06:11.620 --> 00:06:14.060
Confess to your crimes
and those of your accomplices

00:06:14.060 --> 00:06:15.500
and strive for leniency.

00:06:18.839 --> 00:06:19.959
Leniency for what?

00:06:21.399 --> 00:06:25.000
Tell me, what is the sentence
for just robbery?

00:06:25.180 --> 00:06:27.000
At worst, the death penalty, right?

00:06:28.519 --> 00:06:29.899
Kill me now if you dare.

00:06:30.839 --> 00:06:31.959
Do it now. Come on.

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:34.139
Come on.

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:36.224
What are you doing?

00:06:36.459 --> 00:06:38.740
- What are you doing?
- Go ahead, kill me now. Come on, do it.

00:06:39.620 --> 00:06:41.240
Come on, kill me, kill me.

00:06:41.240 --> 00:06:43.779
- Stop it.
- Kill me, kill me.

00:06:43.779 --> 00:06:44.339
Let go.

00:06:45.399 --> 00:06:45.939
Let go.

00:06:45.939 --> 00:06:48.959
The cops are torturing me.
You got all that on tape, right?

00:06:48.959 --> 00:06:52.560
Just... kill me, kill me.

00:07:19.899 --> 00:07:20.620
Take him away.

00:07:21.620 --> 00:07:22.220
Shut up.

00:07:24.360 --> 00:07:25.240
Shut up. Go.

00:07:31.872 --> 00:07:35.040
(Crack down on crime.
Protect the people.)

00:07:39.104 --> 00:07:39.800
(3rd Interrogation)

00:07:39.800 --> 00:07:41.120
Like I said before.

00:07:42.740 --> 00:07:43.939
If it weren't for you,

00:07:44.639 --> 00:07:47.000
I might've spent my whole life
in Shaguai Village.

00:07:47.519 --> 00:07:48.459
All these years,

00:07:49.339 --> 00:07:51.500
you've always suspected me,
and I've put up with it.

00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:55.779
But now you're coming after my buddy.

00:07:58.399 --> 00:08:01.180
I know you can't let go
of Officer Lin's case.

00:08:03.180 --> 00:08:06.560
You're even raising his daughter now,
seeing her every day.

00:08:07.459 --> 00:08:10.459
Officer Zhu, you've got some issues
bottled up, right?

00:08:10.680 --> 00:08:11.560
Meng Guangcai,

00:08:12.279 --> 00:08:13.939
answer the questions properly.

00:08:14.220 --> 00:08:15.279
Don't ramble.

00:08:16.180 --> 00:08:17.019
My apologies.

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:21.060
Am I not allowed
to mention Officer Lin anymore?

00:08:22.839 --> 00:08:24.060
There's nothing you can't say.

00:08:25.939 --> 00:08:29.339
And you'd never guess the reason
we found the evidence to nail you

00:08:30.459 --> 00:08:32.080
does connect back to Lin Shan.

00:08:34.879 --> 00:08:36.059
Didn't I tell you?

00:08:36.259 --> 00:08:37.879
Without solid proof,

00:08:38.559 --> 00:08:41.000
we wouldn't bring
a big boss like you in here.

00:08:42.320 --> 00:08:44.320
You must have been wondering
all these days

00:08:45.179 --> 00:08:49.940
what it is that pins you
to the 6.10 case, right?

00:08:59.179 --> 00:09:00.259
It's your son,

00:09:02.179 --> 00:09:03.000
Meng Xiaoliang.

00:09:08.879 --> 00:09:11.000
Meng Xiaoliang
had a medical check-up recently.

00:09:11.759 --> 00:09:13.139
His test results

00:09:13.259 --> 00:09:17.299
were compared to the blood sample left
by a suspect at the 6.10 crime scene.

00:09:17.700 --> 00:09:20.440
The two blood samples
indicate a father-son relationship.

00:09:21.379 --> 00:09:25.259
Meaning you, Meng Guangcai,
are a prime suspect.

00:09:29.259 --> 00:09:31.500
It's been 18 years, Guangcai.

00:09:32.179 --> 00:09:34.259
The robbery happened 18 years ago.

00:09:34.759 --> 00:09:38.259
Did you really think the truth
was buried forever, with no trace left?

00:09:38.940 --> 00:09:42.000
But don't forget,
justice has a long arm.

00:09:43.080 --> 00:09:44.679
Maybe this is fate.

00:09:45.759 --> 00:09:47.700
You thought your plan was flawless,

00:09:48.440 --> 00:09:51.940
but in the end, it was your own son
who exposed you.

00:09:53.080 --> 00:09:53.879
Officer Zhu,

00:09:56.379 --> 00:09:57.740
no matter what you say,

00:09:59.200 --> 00:10:00.379
what I need to say is

00:10:01.379 --> 00:10:02.200
that I

00:10:02.879 --> 00:10:04.620
have nothing to do with the 6.10 case.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:06.679
I didn't rob anyone.

00:10:07.379 --> 00:10:09.500
I am innocent.

00:10:13.740 --> 00:10:14.379
Captain Li.

00:10:15.440 --> 00:10:16.700
We'll talk later.

00:10:17.240 --> 00:10:18.000
We found something.

00:10:25.632 --> 00:10:29.745
(Meng Xiaoliang and Meng Guangcai
are not biologically father and son.)

00:10:29.879 --> 00:10:32.259
Meng Guangcai is not
Meng Xiaoliang's father.

00:10:38.120 --> 00:10:42.240
The blood at the crime scene belonged
to Meng Xiaoliang's father.

00:10:42.759 --> 00:10:44.759
That was our basis
for going after Meng Guangcai.

00:10:45.059 --> 00:10:46.559
Now it's all messed up.

00:10:46.559 --> 00:10:48.120
This report

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:50.580
doesn't pin down Meng Guangcai,

00:10:50.879 --> 00:10:52.759
but at least we caught Wang Dazhu.

00:10:53.080 --> 00:10:55.139
It isn't entirely fruitless, right?

00:10:55.500 --> 00:10:58.679
His reaction was off.
His reaction was completely off.

00:10:59.000 --> 00:11:02.080
After he learned the evidence
was Meng Xiaoliang's blood, he relaxed.

00:11:03.139 --> 00:11:05.820
Could he have known all along
that Xiaoliang isn't his son?

00:11:06.580 --> 00:11:09.940
I think we need to stick to evidence.
No wild guesses.

00:11:10.679 --> 00:11:12.440
The blood sample is evidence.

00:11:13.000 --> 00:11:14.320
The only thing we know for sure

00:11:14.580 --> 00:11:16.879
is whoever Meng Xiaoliang's father is,

00:11:17.059 --> 00:11:19.379
he definitely
took part in the robbery, right?

00:11:19.580 --> 00:11:22.320
So who is his real father?

00:11:24.559 --> 00:11:25.500
Who is the father?

00:11:27.759 --> 00:11:28.820
The mother knows best.

00:11:29.580 --> 00:11:31.940
Bring Xue Qin in for questioning
and we'll find out.

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:33.940
Okay, it's settled then.

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:37.440
Zhou, come with me to see Xue Qin.

00:11:37.440 --> 00:11:38.179
Sir,

00:11:39.679 --> 00:11:40.580
let me go with you.

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:42.940
I'm an old acquaintance of her.

00:11:43.580 --> 00:11:44.879
It'll make questioning easier.

00:11:46.320 --> 00:11:46.820
Let's go.

00:11:48.259 --> 00:11:52.379
Police have not disclosed the reason
for Mr. Meng's detention so far.

00:11:52.759 --> 00:11:54.759
Mr. Jiao, can you
shed some light on this?

00:11:55.379 --> 00:11:56.679
Let me correct your wording.

00:11:57.179 --> 00:11:58.000
It's not detention.

00:11:58.759 --> 00:12:01.580
Mr. Meng is cooperating
with the investigation as a witness.

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:05.500
We have full confidence in Mr. Meng.

00:12:05.940 --> 00:12:06.580
Four words:

00:12:07.379 --> 00:12:08.740
Cooperate with the investigation.

00:12:08.940 --> 00:12:11.179
Now, many online sources claim

00:12:11.379 --> 00:12:15.639
that Mr. Meng is a victim
of retaliation by a certain Officer Zhu.

00:12:15.879 --> 00:12:17.879
What's your take on this rumor?

00:12:18.759 --> 00:12:20.440
I have no idea about that.

00:12:20.440 --> 00:12:24.379
But I believe the police's procedures
are lawful and compliant.

00:12:25.700 --> 00:12:28.440
As for that officer's motives,

00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:30.139
or if he was instructed by...

00:12:31.440 --> 00:12:33.240
Well, you can investigate that.

00:12:33.759 --> 00:12:38.320
After all, some people in business
will do anything to achieve their goals.

00:12:39.240 --> 00:12:41.740
Regarding the investigation results
released by the police,

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:42.820
once we get them,

00:12:42.820 --> 00:12:45.700
we will promptly provide an explanation
to the public and shareholders.

00:12:45.879 --> 00:12:47.179
Let's wait and see together.

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:51.820
Officer Zhu is here,
in Ms. Xue's office.

00:12:53.440 --> 00:12:54.259
Okay.

00:12:56.440 --> 00:12:57.440
Zhu,

00:12:58.879 --> 00:12:59.759
didn't the officers

00:13:00.179 --> 00:13:02.500
already ask all that when they came?

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:04.879
Quite a few reporters are here.

00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:09.940
Caisheng Group's been
pretty lively lately.

00:13:10.639 --> 00:13:12.240
They all came on their own.

00:13:12.759 --> 00:13:13.759
I don't know much.

00:13:14.440 --> 00:13:16.559
My colleagues at the company
are handling it.

00:13:16.759 --> 00:13:20.580
Xue Qin, there have been
some new developments in the case.

00:13:21.080 --> 00:13:22.139
We were also surprised.

00:13:22.940 --> 00:13:24.000
So we came to ask you.

00:13:24.139 --> 00:13:28.240
Your son Meng Xiaoliang and your husband
are not biologically related.

00:13:28.679 --> 00:13:29.500
Did you know that?

00:13:40.500 --> 00:13:42.179
Let me restate the question.

00:13:42.440 --> 00:13:45.879
Meng Guangcai is not your son's father.
Were you aware of this?

00:14:00.139 --> 00:14:02.820
Tell us, who is Meng Xiaoliang's father?

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:09.320
I don't know.

00:14:14.820 --> 00:14:16.620
Please answer the questions truthfully.

00:14:17.379 --> 00:14:19.000
I truly don't know.

00:14:20.080 --> 00:14:20.879
Qin,

00:14:23.240 --> 00:14:24.240
calm down first.

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:25.940
There's no rush.

00:14:26.759 --> 00:14:29.000
Take your time to think and speak.

00:14:30.179 --> 00:14:31.139
I never

00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:35.700
told anyone about this matter.

00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:39.320
My family didn't know.

00:14:41.259 --> 00:14:43.080
Xue Qin, you can rest assured.

00:14:43.440 --> 00:14:46.879
Everything we talk about today
is strictly confidential.

00:14:47.379 --> 00:14:51.700
It has a direct bearing
on the investigation into your husband.

00:14:52.639 --> 00:14:54.620
We hope you will answer truthfully.

00:14:56.000 --> 00:14:59.200
So tell us, who exactly
is Meng Xiaoliang's father?

00:15:00.879 --> 00:15:03.440
Xiaoliang seems to be about a year older
than Qianqian.

00:15:04.120 --> 00:15:07.580
But Xiaoliang
started school a year early.

00:15:08.580 --> 00:15:10.580
He was born in 1992.

00:15:11.080 --> 00:15:13.440
Going back one more year,
that would be 1991.

00:15:14.759 --> 00:15:15.620
Think again.

00:15:16.580 --> 00:15:17.379
Think again.

00:15:18.740 --> 00:15:19.879
It was 1991.

00:15:22.059 --> 00:15:24.259
I was working at the video theater
in Magou Town.

00:15:26.320 --> 00:15:28.320
One day, on my way back to the village,

00:15:32.379 --> 00:15:34.259
someone suddenly jumped out
from behind me.

00:15:37.460 --> 00:15:37.960
Move!

00:15:38.379 --> 00:15:38.879
Move!

00:15:38.879 --> 00:15:41.240
Help! Someone, help!

00:15:45.620 --> 00:15:46.700
Who was that person?

00:15:47.879 --> 00:15:49.440
I passed out at the time.

00:15:51.759 --> 00:15:52.639
I didn't see.

00:15:53.240 --> 00:15:55.120
Did you tell anyone about it back then?

00:15:56.259 --> 00:15:57.500
Did you call the police?

00:15:58.320 --> 00:15:59.740
When something like that happened,

00:16:02.500 --> 00:16:04.320
I was terrified at the time.

00:16:05.759 --> 00:16:07.179
I didn't dare tell anyone.

00:16:07.379 --> 00:16:10.259
Did you have any enemies back then?

00:16:17.820 --> 00:16:20.200
Back then, Guangcai and the others
went to work in Beiyan.

00:16:20.820 --> 00:16:22.940
Principal Chen's eyes
were getting worse.

00:16:23.580 --> 00:16:25.379
I stayed at the video theater,

00:16:25.879 --> 00:16:27.759
hoping to work some night shifts

00:16:29.080 --> 00:16:31.940
to earn some overtime pay
for his treatment.

00:16:33.379 --> 00:16:35.879
If you insist we had enemies...

00:16:42.240 --> 00:16:43.700
You should remember, Zhu.

00:16:47.740 --> 00:16:49.580
Are you saying

00:16:50.740 --> 00:16:51.580
it was Zuo Long?

00:16:53.379 --> 00:16:54.440
I'm not sure.

00:16:56.700 --> 00:16:59.440
I worked at the video theater every day.

00:16:59.440 --> 00:17:01.639
I didn't really know anyone else.

00:17:03.139 --> 00:17:04.700
How could I have enemies?

00:17:05.579 --> 00:17:06.940
After such a major incident,

00:17:07.859 --> 00:17:10.819
you didn't tell anyone
and decided to have the child.

00:17:11.480 --> 00:17:12.440
Why is that?

00:17:15.200 --> 00:17:16.859
I wanted to have an abortion.

00:17:18.859 --> 00:17:20.440
But the doctor told me

00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:24.859
if I had an abortion,

00:17:25.440 --> 00:17:27.319
I might never get pregnant again.

00:17:29.500 --> 00:17:31.740
Did anyone else know about this?

00:17:32.500 --> 00:17:33.220
No.

00:17:34.440 --> 00:17:35.319
Meng Guangcai.

00:17:36.460 --> 00:17:37.319
Did he know?

00:17:42.359 --> 00:17:43.359
He didn't know.

00:17:45.799 --> 00:17:46.900
I didn't dare tell him.

00:17:48.519 --> 00:17:49.200
Xue Qin,

00:17:49.700 --> 00:17:51.240
I must remind you,

00:17:52.019 --> 00:17:55.880
you are obligated to answer
all my questions truthfully.

00:17:56.140 --> 00:18:00.299
If you conceal, give false testimony,
or withhold information,

00:18:00.299 --> 00:18:01.859
you will be held legally responsible.

00:18:02.119 --> 00:18:05.460
So, are you sure
that what you've said is true?

00:18:12.759 --> 00:18:13.680
I am sure.

00:18:21.319 --> 00:18:22.000
Zhu.

00:18:26.140 --> 00:18:28.740
Officer, can I talk with him in private?

00:18:29.019 --> 00:18:30.000
We can talk here.

00:18:30.259 --> 00:18:31.220
He's my superior.

00:18:31.680 --> 00:18:34.880
Some matters might not be clear
without him here.

00:18:35.460 --> 00:18:36.059
Okay.

00:18:37.140 --> 00:18:37.859
Zhu,

00:18:38.400 --> 00:18:40.460
you took Guangcai away publicly.

00:18:40.819 --> 00:18:42.619
It's caused quite a stir
within the group

00:18:42.900 --> 00:18:44.519
and put Qin under a lot of pressure.

00:18:45.859 --> 00:18:47.460
We go way back.

00:18:47.819 --> 00:18:50.799
We've all seen the misunderstandings
between you and Guangcai these years.

00:18:51.299 --> 00:18:53.119
Even if you are the police,

00:18:53.400 --> 00:18:54.819
isn't targeting Guangcai enough?

00:18:55.140 --> 00:18:56.619
Why make things hard for a woman?

00:18:58.859 --> 00:18:59.619
Jiao Lijun,

00:19:00.359 --> 00:19:02.680
you know how investigations work, right?

00:19:03.079 --> 00:19:03.839
Look.

00:19:04.359 --> 00:19:07.299
My superior has been very clear.

00:19:07.819 --> 00:19:10.400
There's no need for us to say more.

00:19:10.980 --> 00:19:11.579
Lijun,

00:19:12.640 --> 00:19:13.799
let me give you some advice.

00:19:14.059 --> 00:19:15.880
Something major happened
within your group.

00:19:16.299 --> 00:19:19.619
You should think more
about your own involvement in this.

00:19:20.579 --> 00:19:22.680
And you're still concerned
about Guangcai's wife?

00:19:28.640 --> 00:19:29.140
Alright.

00:19:30.140 --> 00:19:30.759
Officer Zhu,

00:19:31.380 --> 00:19:32.500
I formally inform you.

00:19:33.140 --> 00:19:35.519
I am now the acting head
of Caisheng Group.

00:19:36.119 --> 00:19:39.220
If you have more questions later,
please come to me first.

00:19:39.619 --> 00:19:42.400
The legal department and I
will be ready to assist.

00:19:47.619 --> 00:19:48.319
Master,

00:19:48.640 --> 00:19:51.859
Xue Qin's story stands on its own
and is completely flawless.

00:19:52.640 --> 00:19:54.339
That's precisely why it's suspicious.

00:19:55.720 --> 00:19:57.519
It can't be proven true or false.

00:19:57.519 --> 00:19:59.019
She says she was raped.

00:19:59.559 --> 00:20:00.980
But there was no witness.

00:20:01.900 --> 00:20:03.140
Usually in such cases,

00:20:03.259 --> 00:20:04.680
either she's telling the truth,

00:20:04.680 --> 00:20:07.460
or every word she says
has been meticulously crafted

00:20:07.460 --> 00:20:09.019
to smooth over all potential flaws.

00:20:09.299 --> 00:20:10.079
What do you think?

00:20:10.380 --> 00:20:11.519
I prefer the latter.

00:20:14.059 --> 00:20:16.099
Xue Qin said Zuo Long raped her.

00:20:16.400 --> 00:20:19.880
Meng Guangcai and Wang Dazhu also said
Zuo Long was involved in the robbery.

00:20:20.400 --> 00:20:21.579
It's too coincidental.

00:20:22.960 --> 00:20:26.119
Thinking back now, ever since I started
working with you on criminal cases,

00:20:26.119 --> 00:20:28.319
you've been talking
about Meng Guangcai every day.

00:20:28.319 --> 00:20:31.079
The more you talked,
the more suspicious he seemed.

00:20:31.200 --> 00:20:34.380
Now, they all seem inscrutable,
like they came prepared.

00:20:34.380 --> 00:20:37.000
Master, weren't you and him buddies
when you were younger?

00:20:37.480 --> 00:20:39.119
How did you first start suspecting him?

00:20:42.579 --> 00:20:43.900
(Baima Building Materials Market, 1995)
For tiles,

00:20:43.900 --> 00:20:45.259
just use that color.

00:20:45.839 --> 00:20:48.339
Look, the third one. That color is good.

00:20:48.440 --> 00:20:48.980
Yes.

00:20:49.680 --> 00:20:51.319
That one will match the kitchen well.

00:20:51.319 --> 00:20:51.960
Xue Qin.

00:20:54.559 --> 00:20:56.180
Zhu, what brings you here?

00:20:56.180 --> 00:20:57.619
- Your place
- You didn't tell me.

00:20:57.619 --> 00:20:58.496
wasn't hard to find.

00:20:59.579 --> 00:21:01.259
I haven't come since the opening.

00:21:01.259 --> 00:21:03.819
I had some business nearby,
so I dropped by.

00:21:04.940 --> 00:21:05.859
- Not bad.
- Let me make you some tea.

00:21:05.859 --> 00:21:07.400
No, don't trouble yourself.

00:21:07.960 --> 00:21:10.380
I'm just impressed. It's really nice.

00:21:11.319 --> 00:21:12.359
This whole area, right?

00:21:12.359 --> 00:21:13.799
No, this is the office.

00:21:13.799 --> 00:21:14.460
- And...
- The office.

00:21:14.460 --> 00:21:16.319
Right here. This area is ours.

00:21:16.319 --> 00:21:17.299
This is the shop?

00:21:17.400 --> 00:21:18.099
Yes.

00:21:18.519 --> 00:21:20.140
This is quite a scale you've got.

00:21:20.400 --> 00:21:21.599
It's alright.

00:21:23.059 --> 00:21:23.720
Xue Qin,

00:21:24.480 --> 00:21:25.700
it's only been a few years.

00:21:26.299 --> 00:21:28.500
You've become the lady running the shop.

00:21:29.019 --> 00:21:30.859
And Guangcai's a small boss now.

00:21:31.119 --> 00:21:33.099
And the size of your business
is not small at all.

00:21:33.480 --> 00:21:34.519
So, are you making money?

00:21:35.079 --> 00:21:37.720
Not bad.
I see they're pretty busy every day.

00:21:37.720 --> 00:21:38.759
Must be profitable.

00:21:39.880 --> 00:21:41.000
These tiles are yours?

00:21:41.000 --> 00:21:41.680
Yes.

00:21:43.339 --> 00:21:44.680
The quality looks good.

00:21:45.640 --> 00:21:46.220
Xue Qin,

00:21:46.619 --> 00:21:49.799
actually, my kitchen
needs a proper renovation.

00:21:49.799 --> 00:21:51.079
I'll buy the tiles from you.

00:21:51.299 --> 00:21:52.680
Right here from your shop.

00:21:52.859 --> 00:21:55.640
Otherwise, Huifen keeps saying
I don't care about home.

00:21:55.640 --> 00:21:57.180
You're too kind, Zhu.

00:21:57.180 --> 00:21:58.839
I'll sort this out for you.

00:21:58.980 --> 00:22:01.900
See? Doing business makes you
more generous. So different.

00:22:04.799 --> 00:22:05.880
That's Xiaoliang, right?

00:22:05.880 --> 00:22:08.099
Yes. Xiaoliang, say "Uncle".

00:22:08.099 --> 00:22:09.000
He's gotten so big.

00:22:09.000 --> 00:22:10.339
"Uncle"? I'm older than that.

00:22:10.339 --> 00:22:10.880
Xiaoliang.

00:22:12.819 --> 00:22:14.180
Look at him.

00:22:14.759 --> 00:22:17.079
He seems timid,
not like Guangcai at all.

00:22:17.359 --> 00:22:18.720
Who does he take after?

00:22:19.299 --> 00:22:21.299
Xiaoliang has been frail
since he was little.

00:22:21.960 --> 00:22:24.240
I spend more time with him. He's shy.

00:22:25.359 --> 00:22:28.880
Xue Qin, I heard Guangcai borrowed money

00:22:29.380 --> 00:22:33.220
from his boss in Guangnan
to pay for Xiaoliang's surgery, right?

00:22:35.259 --> 00:22:38.680
Guangcai really went all out for him.

00:22:41.460 --> 00:22:42.099
Enough talk.

00:22:43.500 --> 00:22:45.519
Alright, I've got some things to do.

00:22:46.059 --> 00:22:47.759
Guangcai doesn't seem
to be returning soon.

00:22:47.859 --> 00:22:48.640
I'll go back.

00:22:48.839 --> 00:22:49.960
- You...
- See you.

00:22:49.960 --> 00:22:51.519
But you just got here.

00:22:51.519 --> 00:22:54.220
You and Guangcai
can bring Xiaoliang over to my place.

00:22:54.299 --> 00:22:55.519
- I'll cook for you.
- Okay.

00:22:55.519 --> 00:22:56.640
And you can see my kitchen.

00:22:56.640 --> 00:22:57.299
Sounds good.

00:22:58.319 --> 00:22:59.380
You've counted them all?

00:22:59.380 --> 00:23:00.079
Listen here.

00:23:00.140 --> 00:23:02.079
If I find one tile missing,
you owe me three.

00:23:02.079 --> 00:23:02.740
Understood?

00:23:02.900 --> 00:23:03.759
Don't worry.

00:23:04.119 --> 00:23:06.299
And chipped ones too.
You'll replace every single one.

00:23:06.480 --> 00:23:07.319
Rest assured.

00:23:14.559 --> 00:23:16.720
Come on, shut it down. Shut it down.

00:23:16.880 --> 00:23:18.819
Who are you trying to impress?

00:23:19.140 --> 00:23:19.980
Think you're tough?

00:23:19.980 --> 00:23:24.640
Hongliang, no.
I'm just hauling some terrazzo to sell.

00:23:29.000 --> 00:23:29.960
Move it.

00:23:33.299 --> 00:23:34.720
It's all terrazzo.

00:23:35.900 --> 00:23:37.799
Who said you could sell terrazzo?

00:23:38.960 --> 00:23:43.619
But no one said we couldn't before.

00:23:43.960 --> 00:23:44.819
No one said so, huh?

00:23:44.819 --> 00:23:45.460
That's right.

00:23:45.720 --> 00:23:46.400
Stop looking.

00:23:46.400 --> 00:23:47.400
Unload it and smash it.

00:23:47.559 --> 00:23:50.119
No! Hongliang, please don't!

00:23:50.119 --> 00:23:51.700
- I already paid it.
- What?

00:23:51.700 --> 00:23:52.819
What? You want to fight?

00:23:52.819 --> 00:23:55.759
No, not at all. I won't sell it, okay?

00:23:55.880 --> 00:23:56.799
I won't bring it back.

00:24:02.220 --> 00:24:06.099
I run this market. Sell anything
after getting my permission. Got it?

00:24:07.180 --> 00:24:08.019
Do you hear me?

00:24:08.019 --> 00:24:08.640
Yes.

00:24:10.079 --> 00:24:10.880
Fatty.

00:24:13.559 --> 00:24:14.119
Let's go.

00:24:22.656 --> 00:24:30.080
(Shaguai Building Materials Store)

00:24:31.380 --> 00:24:32.099
Where's the cargo?

00:24:32.099 --> 00:24:32.960
They stopped me.

00:24:34.299 --> 00:24:35.259
What happened?

00:24:36.480 --> 00:24:40.680
Qin, everyone knows terrazzo
is the big money-maker now.

00:24:40.900 --> 00:24:43.619
The Hao brothers made it clear.

00:24:43.619 --> 00:24:46.119
Only they get to profit from this.
No one else can sell it.

00:24:46.819 --> 00:24:50.140
Take our money and won't let us sell?
That's bullying.

00:24:51.019 --> 00:24:52.900
Might as well just rob us outright.

00:24:52.900 --> 00:24:55.299
Keep it down.
We can discuss this calmly.

00:24:56.380 --> 00:24:57.359
Let's all be careful.

00:24:57.359 --> 00:24:59.119
This is the latest terrazzo.

00:24:59.119 --> 00:25:01.299
Don't make trouble for Guangcai.
Wait till he's back.

00:25:02.079 --> 00:25:03.259
What's that?

00:25:04.680 --> 00:25:09.259
So why can they sell it?

00:25:09.259 --> 00:25:09.859
This one.

00:25:12.859 --> 00:25:13.696
Six of Characters.

00:25:17.339 --> 00:25:17.940
Green Dragon.

00:25:18.680 --> 00:25:22.079
Mr. Hongkang,
here's last month's management fee.

00:25:24.140 --> 00:25:27.839
Congratulations, Mr. Meng.
Doing so well after joining the market.

00:25:27.980 --> 00:25:31.140
It's all thanks to Mr. Hongkang,
Mr. Hongliang, and everyone's support.

00:25:31.640 --> 00:25:32.880
So polite.

00:25:34.119 --> 00:25:38.500
- South Wind.
- Eight of Characters.

00:25:38.500 --> 00:25:41.079
There's something
I'd like to discuss with you.

00:25:41.299 --> 00:25:42.839
Nothing to discuss. Leave us.

00:25:43.240 --> 00:25:43.960
White Dragon.

00:25:44.619 --> 00:25:46.460
It's fine. Go ahead. Say it here.

00:25:46.759 --> 00:25:47.359
Red Dragon.

00:25:49.359 --> 00:25:50.688
Well, back then, the agreement

00:25:50.688 --> 00:25:56.380
was for us to hand over 40 percent
of the first two years' profits.

00:25:57.579 --> 00:26:00.500
We just opened a few months ago.
Money has been really tight.

00:26:03.099 --> 00:26:05.740
Nowadays, everything's tough
in this market.

00:26:07.259 --> 00:26:08.720
I want to discuss something.

00:26:08.839 --> 00:26:12.140
About the ratio,
can it be adjusted a bit?

00:26:13.640 --> 00:26:16.400
Mr. Meng, didn't we agree on this?

00:26:17.579 --> 00:26:20.220
We need to follow rules.

00:26:21.240 --> 00:26:23.460
If we break the rules now,

00:26:23.460 --> 00:26:26.059
how are my brother and I
supposed to maintain our standing?

00:26:26.059 --> 00:26:27.700
We stick to what was decided.

00:26:28.119 --> 00:26:29.319
Don't break the rules.

00:26:30.640 --> 00:26:31.519
Yes.

00:26:32.319 --> 00:26:33.079
Three of Circles.

00:26:33.299 --> 00:26:33.900
Hello?

00:26:35.619 --> 00:26:36.640
Which shop?

00:26:42.559 --> 00:26:44.180
Breaking rules again.

00:26:48.220 --> 00:26:49.460
Stop smashing! Stop!

00:26:49.460 --> 00:26:49.960
Get away!

00:26:49.960 --> 00:26:51.480
Stop smashing! Please!

00:26:51.480 --> 00:26:53.720
Hongkang, stop smashing! Please!

00:26:53.720 --> 00:26:54.319
Stop!

00:26:55.460 --> 00:26:56.799
- Stop smashing!
- Stop smashing!

00:26:57.319 --> 00:26:57.900
Hongkang,

00:26:59.079 --> 00:27:01.519
the terrazzo I'm selling
is different from yours.

00:27:01.519 --> 00:27:02.900
It's cheaper than yours,

00:27:02.900 --> 00:27:03.400
Hongkang.

00:27:03.400 --> 00:27:06.140
You're really putting us brothers
in a tough spot.

00:27:07.079 --> 00:27:10.559
How many times?
Didn't we give you a chance?

00:27:10.759 --> 00:27:11.799
You asked for trouble.

00:27:11.799 --> 00:27:12.319
Yes.

00:27:12.960 --> 00:27:13.799
What did we tell you?

00:27:13.799 --> 00:27:14.640
Hongkang! Hongkang!

00:27:14.640 --> 00:27:15.619
What did we say?

00:27:15.619 --> 00:27:16.579
Hongliang! Hongliang!

00:27:16.819 --> 00:27:17.940
Think you're clever, huh?

00:27:17.940 --> 00:27:18.500
No, no.

00:27:18.559 --> 00:27:20.859
We told you
to sell it exactly as you're told.

00:27:21.359 --> 00:27:22.359
Did you forget that?

00:27:22.599 --> 00:27:25.339
We must teach him a lesson
he won't forget, got it?

00:27:25.339 --> 00:27:26.400
Speak properly.

00:27:28.400 --> 00:27:31.960
Folk merchant, sorry about this.

00:27:32.619 --> 00:27:33.960
We don't want to hit anyone.

00:27:34.180 --> 00:27:36.759
But this market must have rules, right?

00:27:37.359 --> 00:27:38.900
It's written in the contract.

00:27:38.900 --> 00:27:41.019
What it says not to sell,
you don't sell.

00:27:41.619 --> 00:27:44.259
Set the price it says,
and sell it how it should be sold.

00:27:44.259 --> 00:27:47.960
Not following the contract?
He is the best example.

00:27:47.960 --> 00:27:50.960
Don't like it?
In this market, we call the shots.

00:27:51.079 --> 00:27:52.119
Accept it.

00:27:53.019 --> 00:27:54.359
Or get out of here.

00:27:56.099 --> 00:27:56.759
Mr. He.

00:27:56.759 --> 00:27:57.599
Hongkang.

00:27:57.599 --> 00:28:00.440
Well, look at this.

00:28:00.619 --> 00:28:01.900
What's to say? Smash it.

00:28:02.259 --> 00:28:03.059
Smash it. Move.

00:28:03.059 --> 00:28:04.799
Hongkang, stop smashing! Hongkang!

00:28:05.140 --> 00:28:08.400
Hongkang, no! Stop smashing! Stop!

00:28:08.400 --> 00:28:09.400
- Stop, Hongkang!
- Get lost!

00:28:09.400 --> 00:28:10.299
- Stop! Don't smash it!
- Sorry.

00:28:10.299 --> 00:28:10.839
Sorry.

00:28:10.839 --> 00:28:12.559
Stop smashing! Sir! Sir!

00:28:12.559 --> 00:28:14.579
Stop smashing! Stop! Sir!

00:28:16.480 --> 00:28:17.400
Officer,

00:28:18.140 --> 00:28:21.400
it's just a little argument
between merchants in the market.

00:28:21.460 --> 00:28:23.720
How'd a minor dispute trouble you?

00:28:23.720 --> 00:28:24.759
Minor dispute?

00:28:25.000 --> 00:28:27.859
Deliberately destroying property
carries criminal penalties.

00:28:28.019 --> 00:28:30.819
Intentionally hurting someone
is an additional charge.

00:28:30.819 --> 00:28:33.599
Alright, speak up.
Who smashed your shop?

00:28:36.680 --> 00:28:38.759
Mr. He, the officer is asking you.

00:28:46.119 --> 00:28:47.259
Who smashed your shop?

00:28:50.720 --> 00:28:51.680
Not talking?

00:28:52.880 --> 00:28:56.140
Alright then, the person in charge here
comes back with me.

00:28:56.819 --> 00:28:59.640
Officer, no need
to take it this far, right?

00:29:00.579 --> 00:29:04.259
Officer, you might not
know us Hao brothers too well?

00:29:04.259 --> 00:29:06.960
In this market,
we operate strictly by the rules.

00:29:06.960 --> 00:29:08.380
Every shop has a contract.

00:29:08.720 --> 00:29:10.720
And we've dealt with plenty of police.

00:29:10.720 --> 00:29:12.220
Don't make trouble for us on purpose.

00:29:12.480 --> 00:29:15.759
So you're refusing to cooperate
with the police investigation?

00:29:16.019 --> 00:29:18.200
No, Officer, look.

00:29:18.200 --> 00:29:19.680
It's just a minor conflict.

00:29:19.759 --> 00:29:21.980
Do us a favor, and consider us friends.

00:29:22.200 --> 00:29:24.079
We've never mistreated our friends.

00:29:24.079 --> 00:29:26.339
Fine, not talking now?
You. And you. Come with me.

00:29:26.519 --> 00:29:28.339
Why? Didn't we tell you already?

00:29:28.720 --> 00:29:29.619
What are you saying?

00:29:32.460 --> 00:29:33.460
Officer Zhu.

00:29:34.460 --> 00:29:36.559
Officer Zhu, don't be angry.

00:29:38.140 --> 00:29:39.400
What's it to you?

00:29:39.400 --> 00:29:40.859
Mr. Hongliang, don't rush.

00:29:41.259 --> 00:29:43.519
Listen to me. Well, Officer Zhu.

00:29:44.079 --> 00:29:46.400
Actually, the thing is like this.

00:29:48.220 --> 00:29:52.140
Our shop got the same goods
as Mr. He's shop.

00:29:52.859 --> 00:29:55.319
Mr. He wasn't too happy about it
and had some objections.

00:29:55.799 --> 00:29:58.400
Then our guy Dazhu argued
with him a bit.

00:29:58.400 --> 00:30:01.460
I lost my temper and smashed his shop.

00:30:02.299 --> 00:30:04.220
Guangcai, I...

00:30:04.220 --> 00:30:07.900
What? If it weren't for you,
this wouldn't have happened.

00:30:08.380 --> 00:30:08.980
I...

00:30:09.519 --> 00:30:10.720
Don't make things worse here.

00:30:11.019 --> 00:30:11.759
Tell me.

00:30:12.839 --> 00:30:14.319
Who exactly smashed your shop?

00:30:21.000 --> 00:30:21.839
Speak.

00:30:22.819 --> 00:30:23.559
Mr. He,

00:30:24.400 --> 00:30:25.680
first, let me apologize to you.

00:30:26.140 --> 00:30:27.559
I acted impulsively at the time.

00:30:28.140 --> 00:30:31.319
Whatever compensation you need,
I'll definitely pay it, alright?

00:30:32.460 --> 00:30:34.859
See, Officer? What did I tell you?

00:30:34.859 --> 00:30:37.819
Just a small conflict.
We can handle it internally.

00:30:41.599 --> 00:30:43.579
You two, come with me.

00:30:46.319 --> 00:30:47.299
Let's go.

00:30:50.180 --> 00:30:51.180
Let's go.

00:30:59.059 --> 00:31:00.980
I asked everyone at Baima Market.

00:31:00.980 --> 00:31:02.259
Not one person said it was you.

00:31:02.259 --> 00:31:05.019
Even Mr. He only said it was you
when pushed to the limit.

00:31:05.220 --> 00:31:06.720
You think I'm an idiot?

00:31:08.980 --> 00:31:09.819
Zhu,

00:31:10.519 --> 00:31:11.579
calm down.

00:31:12.059 --> 00:31:13.720
We and the shop next door

00:31:14.680 --> 00:31:15.859
had a bit of a disagreement.

00:31:16.819 --> 00:31:19.579
I got angry and lashed out.

00:31:21.380 --> 00:31:23.319
I just came back from your shop today.

00:31:23.559 --> 00:31:25.059
I know you were bullied there.

00:31:25.519 --> 00:31:27.180
No matter what, that wasn't necessary.

00:31:27.680 --> 00:31:28.960
Are you joking?

00:31:29.819 --> 00:31:30.819
No, Zhu.

00:31:31.859 --> 00:31:33.220
Meng Guangcai, tell me.

00:31:34.319 --> 00:31:37.640
Did they put you up to taking the blame?

00:31:37.640 --> 00:31:38.619
Tell me.

00:31:38.960 --> 00:31:40.220
You can say yes or no.

00:31:40.220 --> 00:31:41.019
But I'm warning you.

00:31:41.359 --> 00:31:43.839
If you keep this up,
you're only wasting your own time.

00:31:47.079 --> 00:31:48.619
A man should own up to what he's done.

00:31:49.680 --> 00:31:51.359
I... I've thought it through.

00:31:54.440 --> 00:31:55.519
What happened to you?

00:31:55.519 --> 00:31:56.680
Where's the tough guy I knew?

00:31:57.799 --> 00:31:59.880
After two years away,
I barely recognize you.

00:32:03.400 --> 00:32:03.980
Fine.

00:32:05.180 --> 00:32:06.180
If you want to play dumb,

00:32:06.799 --> 00:32:09.180
you can think it over
during your detention.

00:32:40.032 --> 00:32:42.016
(Detention Center)

00:33:00.720 --> 00:33:01.319
Guangcai, stop.

00:33:01.319 --> 00:33:02.619
Guangcai, don't move.

00:33:03.000 --> 00:33:05.019
Hold on, hold on.

00:33:08.799 --> 00:33:11.680
A prodigal's return is priceless.
Leaving prison, bad luck vanishes.

00:33:12.220 --> 00:33:13.519
Cross the fire, no more fear.

00:33:14.619 --> 00:33:16.519
From now on,
your life will shine brighter.

00:33:18.819 --> 00:33:19.900
Step over, Guangcai.

00:33:41.680 --> 00:33:42.339
Guangcai,

00:33:42.960 --> 00:33:43.819
you've had it rough.

00:33:44.640 --> 00:33:45.180
Hao.

00:33:45.299 --> 00:33:48.319
I appreciate the gesture.
Tonight's on me.

00:33:48.319 --> 00:33:49.480
Let's all go for drinks.

00:33:49.599 --> 00:33:51.180
Come on, get in the car. Let's go.

00:33:52.140 --> 00:33:54.799
You two know the place, right?

00:33:55.079 --> 00:33:56.599
Just run there. We can't fit you.

00:33:57.559 --> 00:33:58.119
Get in.

00:33:58.119 --> 00:33:58.819
Get in.

00:33:59.980 --> 00:34:01.079
We like you.

00:34:03.359 --> 00:34:04.079
Hurry up.

00:34:13.519 --> 00:34:14.019
Hongkang.

00:34:14.019 --> 00:34:14.840
- Come on.
- Come on.

00:34:14.840 --> 00:34:15.559
Thanks, Hongkang.

00:34:18.659 --> 00:34:20.480
Hongliang. Come on, guys.

00:34:20.739 --> 00:34:22.179
Toast Guangcai. Come on.

00:34:22.420 --> 00:34:23.099
Come on.

00:34:23.559 --> 00:34:24.940
- To Guangcai!
- To Guangcai!

00:34:24.940 --> 00:34:26.400
- To Guangcai!
- To Guangcai!

00:34:26.679 --> 00:34:28.320
Thanks, Hongliang. Thanks, brothers.

00:34:34.300 --> 00:34:36.059
No. Don't move.

00:34:36.579 --> 00:34:37.300
Stay put.

00:34:37.980 --> 00:34:39.340
Come on, guys, take a look.

00:34:40.380 --> 00:34:43.219
Fine clothes make the man. Turn around.

00:34:44.519 --> 00:34:45.719
Hongkang bought it specially.

00:34:46.059 --> 00:34:47.300
What does this show?

00:34:47.300 --> 00:34:50.599
From now on, you're one of us,
part of the family.

00:34:51.619 --> 00:34:52.159
Come on, sit.

00:34:52.159 --> 00:34:53.659
Okay. Thanks, Hongliang.

00:34:54.119 --> 00:34:56.800
Hongkang, you're thoughtful.
This outfit must've cost a lot.

00:34:56.800 --> 00:34:58.619
Qin, make sure
to pay Hongkang back later.

00:34:58.860 --> 00:34:59.719
Don't be so formal.

00:34:59.719 --> 00:35:00.659
- Forget about the money.
- Exactly.

00:35:00.659 --> 00:35:01.860
Here, let me top you up.

00:35:01.860 --> 00:35:02.420
Okay.

00:35:03.420 --> 00:35:04.079
Buddies,

00:35:04.920 --> 00:35:06.119
Guangcai is righteous.

00:35:06.940 --> 00:35:10.920
Guangcai, you helped me out.
I owe you now.

00:35:12.119 --> 00:35:12.880
Guangcai,

00:35:14.880 --> 00:35:16.119
the biggest piece of meat

00:35:17.159 --> 00:35:17.739
is yours.

00:35:19.480 --> 00:35:20.579
No, Hongkang.

00:35:21.360 --> 00:35:23.360
It's yours. I'll have this piece.

00:35:23.360 --> 00:35:24.400
I'll eat this small one.

00:35:25.340 --> 00:35:26.579
The small one is enough.

00:35:29.360 --> 00:35:31.440
Actually, Hongkang,

00:35:32.219 --> 00:35:33.659
I've known it clearly.

00:35:34.019 --> 00:35:36.300
From the first day I arrived
at Baima Market, I knew

00:35:36.840 --> 00:35:39.219
you were the biggest boss
at Baima Market.

00:35:40.079 --> 00:35:41.500
Don't mention that, Guangcai.

00:35:41.860 --> 00:35:44.760
Qin, if anything happens
in the market later...

00:35:44.760 --> 00:35:47.079
Guangcai, come straight to us brothers.

00:35:47.079 --> 00:35:49.519
I'll handle everything.
Don't worry, Guangcai.

00:35:49.519 --> 00:35:53.079
Stick with me,
and you'll make money and eat well.

00:35:53.079 --> 00:35:53.664
Eat the meat.

00:35:54.360 --> 00:35:55.059
Okay.

00:35:58.980 --> 00:35:59.659
Well,

00:36:01.360 --> 00:36:02.079
Hongkang,

00:36:02.860 --> 00:36:04.512
I need to talk to you about something.

00:36:04.659 --> 00:36:05.480
Well,

00:36:06.659 --> 00:36:09.380
can we re-discuss the contract
we had before?

00:36:11.360 --> 00:36:13.860
Guangcai, you just got here.

00:36:14.940 --> 00:36:15.760
Let's take it slow.

00:36:16.300 --> 00:36:17.500
There'll be plenty of chances.

00:36:17.980 --> 00:36:18.599
Don't worry.

00:36:22.360 --> 00:36:25.260
Check if it's 300 square meters.

00:36:25.940 --> 00:36:28.159
Mr. He, keeping busy?

00:36:28.679 --> 00:36:30.579
How are you? Feeling better?

00:36:31.940 --> 00:36:33.659
I... I know all about it.

00:36:33.659 --> 00:36:35.300
I'm not selling that terrazzo anymore.

00:36:35.420 --> 00:36:37.760
Look, everything I sell now
is fully compliant.

00:36:38.519 --> 00:36:39.619
Don't get me wrong.

00:36:39.619 --> 00:36:42.099
We have nothing to do
with the market management office.

00:36:42.099 --> 00:36:44.179
I just came to see how you're doing.

00:36:44.179 --> 00:36:46.099
No, I'm not misunderstanding.

00:36:46.219 --> 00:36:47.880
Well, I'm doing fine.

00:36:47.880 --> 00:36:49.679
No matter who asks me today,
I'll say that.

00:36:51.099 --> 00:36:51.880
Mr. He,

00:36:52.760 --> 00:36:57.139
Guangcai seemed to help Hao brothers,
making you feel wronged that day.

00:36:57.619 --> 00:37:00.659
But actually, we entered the market
even later than you,

00:37:01.119 --> 00:37:02.579
and we got bullied, too.

00:37:03.159 --> 00:37:04.300
To be honest with you,

00:37:05.079 --> 00:37:07.820
back then, our shop
also stocked terrazzo.

00:37:07.820 --> 00:37:10.820
If Guangcai hadn't done that,
everyone would've suffered later.

00:37:12.659 --> 00:37:13.920
Guangcai just got out.

00:37:14.760 --> 00:37:17.360
He felt really bad about it.

00:37:17.840 --> 00:37:20.119
But he's a man and not good with words.

00:37:20.480 --> 00:37:22.099
So I thought I'd come see you for him.

00:37:23.480 --> 00:37:26.920
We're neighbors doing business.
Don't hold a grudge.

00:37:26.940 --> 00:37:27.760
No, not at all.

00:37:31.340 --> 00:37:34.500
Guangcai, you and the workers
take a break and have some water.

00:37:34.659 --> 00:37:35.619
It's fine, Huifen.

00:37:35.619 --> 00:37:36.840
- The water is here.
- No need.

00:37:37.659 --> 00:37:39.340
Hurry, drink it up.

00:37:39.920 --> 00:37:41.579
The tiling looks really nice.

00:37:41.659 --> 00:37:44.659
The workmanship is good,
and the tiles are of good quality.

00:37:45.619 --> 00:37:47.320
And you gave us such a good price.

00:37:47.519 --> 00:37:50.179
Guangcai, I really owe this to you.

00:37:50.719 --> 00:37:51.340
Huifen,

00:37:51.579 --> 00:37:54.000
our shop can handle
all small jobs like this.

00:37:54.440 --> 00:37:57.480
If you hadn't insisted on paying,
we'd have done this as a favor.

00:37:57.480 --> 00:37:59.260
No way, you have costs too.

00:37:59.260 --> 00:38:00.599
Yours is a small shop.

00:38:01.980 --> 00:38:03.519
Zhu? Zhu?

00:38:04.800 --> 00:38:07.500
Come out and greet Guangcai.

00:38:07.679 --> 00:38:09.000
Stop just sitting there.

00:38:09.679 --> 00:38:11.159
That's just how he is.

00:38:11.420 --> 00:38:13.900
Just sitting there
like a telephone pole every day.

00:38:14.099 --> 00:38:14.760
It's fine.

00:38:14.760 --> 00:38:16.900
Don't mind him. Here's what we'll do.

00:38:17.840 --> 00:38:20.239
I'll go buy some groceries,
and then we'll all eat at home.

00:38:20.239 --> 00:38:20.760
Okay, sure.

00:38:20.760 --> 00:38:21.519
You've worked hard.

00:38:21.519 --> 00:38:22.019
Okay.

00:38:22.340 --> 00:38:23.340
Alright, I'm off then.

00:38:23.860 --> 00:38:27.019
Zhu, come out and talk with Guangcai.

00:38:28.920 --> 00:38:30.079
I'm going to buy groceries.

00:38:59.380 --> 00:39:01.119
Zhu, do you want to check the tiles?

00:39:01.119 --> 00:39:02.420
See if you like the color?

00:39:03.719 --> 00:39:05.860
I just mentioned it casually
to Qin last time.

00:39:06.300 --> 00:39:07.480
She took it seriously.

00:39:09.420 --> 00:39:10.659
Huifen was so happy.

00:39:11.420 --> 00:39:12.099
Thanks.

00:39:12.719 --> 00:39:13.659
Don't mention it.

00:39:13.940 --> 00:39:14.920
Come on, Guangcai, sit.

00:39:15.440 --> 00:39:17.019
If it weren't for the tiling,

00:39:18.019 --> 00:39:19.300
weren't you planning to come?

00:39:20.260 --> 00:39:21.440
Or were you afraid to come?

00:39:23.639 --> 00:39:25.480
What do you mean by that, Zhu?

00:39:26.219 --> 00:39:27.840
I've just been really busy lately.

00:39:28.099 --> 00:39:30.239
The shop's small,
but there's a lot to do.

00:39:30.980 --> 00:39:32.340
Yeah, being your own boss,

00:39:33.019 --> 00:39:36.619
earning money isn't easy.
Now you know it's hard work.

00:39:37.920 --> 00:39:38.599
Yeah.

00:39:39.860 --> 00:39:41.159
Zhu, sit. I'll return to work.

00:39:41.159 --> 00:39:41.719
Guangcai.

00:39:43.360 --> 00:39:45.119
I've been busy lately.
You've been busy, too.

00:39:45.800 --> 00:39:47.119
We haven't had time to chat.

00:39:47.860 --> 00:39:49.860
Tell me more
about your time in Guangnan.

00:39:55.019 --> 00:39:58.139
What's wrong, Zhu?
I mentioned it last time.

00:39:59.219 --> 00:40:00.619
It's a bit awkward to talk about.

00:40:02.119 --> 00:40:04.860
In Guangnan, I worked for one boss

00:40:05.619 --> 00:40:07.840
and did some business
with smuggled goods.

00:40:07.840 --> 00:40:10.360
I know. You told me that.

00:40:11.599 --> 00:40:13.559
You got an advance from that boss

00:40:13.920 --> 00:40:16.360
to pay for Principal Chen's
and Xiaoliang's surgery.

00:40:16.800 --> 00:40:17.659
But Guangcai,

00:40:19.019 --> 00:40:20.119
I recently happened to

00:40:21.840 --> 00:40:22.739
hear something.

00:40:22.920 --> 00:40:23.760
What thing?

00:40:26.420 --> 00:40:31.840
I heard the surgery alone for Xiaoliang
cost 20,000 to 30,000.

00:40:33.719 --> 00:40:35.119
Right.

00:40:35.599 --> 00:40:37.880
I remember you told me

00:40:38.400 --> 00:40:41.079
you arrived in Guangnan
in late June 1993.

00:40:41.860 --> 00:40:44.940
And Xiaoliang had the surgery
in mid-July 1993.

00:40:45.619 --> 00:40:47.340
That's only half a month in between.

00:40:48.079 --> 00:40:51.019
Minus the two or three days
on the train,

00:40:52.059 --> 00:40:54.659
that leaves only about ten days.
How was it so fast?

00:40:59.599 --> 00:41:01.900
I was really desperate back then.

00:41:03.119 --> 00:41:04.519
I... I saw that boss

00:41:05.260 --> 00:41:06.784
making a lot of money from business.

00:41:07.659 --> 00:41:09.019
After working for him a few days,

00:41:09.920 --> 00:41:12.300
I told him about my family situation.

00:41:12.920 --> 00:41:14.159
I begged him for a loan.

00:41:15.659 --> 00:41:18.219
That amount
was probably small change to him.

00:41:18.619 --> 00:41:19.880
He really lent it to me.

00:41:25.340 --> 00:41:26.360
What was his surname?

00:41:26.599 --> 00:41:27.420
Wu.

00:41:29.079 --> 00:41:30.900
But his business
wasn't exactly legitimate.

00:41:31.619 --> 00:41:33.599
I don't know if it was his real surname.

00:41:38.940 --> 00:41:41.360
Well, Zhu,
I... I should get back to work.

00:41:41.360 --> 00:41:42.119
Guangcai.

00:41:48.659 --> 00:41:50.219
You're telling me the truth, right?

00:41:52.159 --> 00:41:53.420
Of course it's the truth, Zhu.

00:42:02.840 --> 00:42:03.619
Guangcai,

00:42:04.920 --> 00:42:06.500
we've known each other so many years.

00:42:06.880 --> 00:42:09.260
Don't do anything you shouldn't,
no matter what.

00:42:12.079 --> 00:42:13.420
Of course not, Zhu.

00:42:19.519 --> 00:42:20.659
I'll get back to work.

00:42:23.840 --> 00:42:24.440
Well?

00:42:33.500 --> 00:42:34.559
How much for the celery?

00:42:34.920 --> 00:42:36.019
Fifteen cents.

00:42:36.019 --> 00:42:37.300
I'll take all of these then.

00:42:37.300 --> 00:42:37.900
Alright.

00:42:37.900 --> 00:42:38.599
Okay, thanks.

00:42:38.599 --> 00:42:39.119
Okay.

00:42:53.099 --> 00:42:53.900
Where's Guangcai?

00:42:55.300 --> 00:42:56.659
Something came up and he left.

00:42:56.920 --> 00:42:58.400
What?

00:42:58.599 --> 00:43:00.500
We agreed on it. I bought so much food.

00:43:00.500 --> 00:43:02.139
I thought he'd drink with you tonight.

00:43:03.800 --> 00:43:06.432
What kind of friend
would lend such a large sum of money

00:43:07.680 --> 00:43:09.619
after knowing someone
for only a few days?

00:43:09.860 --> 00:43:13.000
Stop overthinking.
You're so stressed that you can't sleep.

00:43:13.360 --> 00:43:15.159
Look, I've already bought the food.

00:43:15.360 --> 00:43:17.300
I'll cook
a couple of my signature dishes.

00:43:17.880 --> 00:43:19.579
The workers are also all here.

00:43:19.579 --> 00:43:22.059
How about we have them
join you for a drink tonight?

00:43:34.260 --> 00:43:39.284
=The Silent Rift=